    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S54 platform. This 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features six individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a razor-sharp throttle response. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock. Enthusiast-owned, this vehicle has received critical preventative maintenance including a reinforced rear subframe, rod bearing replacement, and a full VANOS bulletproofing. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing factory-spec dampers and upgraded bushings for superior lateral grip. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with its 'good' status, the drivetrain is optimized for peak performance and longevity.",
      "price": 32500.0,
